title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“PLEASE NOT PLACE ARTICLES OR SIT ON BED.” [Sign placed on a bed in the Mayo Clinic, Rochester, Minnesota, just before it is to be made up for an incoming patient. Submitted by John R. Starrs, Detroit.]
